what is Vue? Vue is an opensource, progressive javascript framework that is used to build user interfaces and Single Page applications (SPA's).


why use vue?
easy to use/ implement and learn.
Performance - lightweight since it doesn't consume too much resources


Official documentation? vuejs.org


Practical
Use Vue 2.7.7

Vue syntaxes;
D.O.M - Document Object Manipulation.


{{}} interpolation [ inserts reactive data into the DOM ]
V-model [ two way data binding ]
V-for [ used for looping in vue ]